Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.33,0:00:05.33,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Vrátil som sa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:07.33,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.19,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:14.06,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san, vrátil som sa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:17.71,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Zaspala?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:20.48,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san, vrátil som...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.47,0:00:38.17,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira, vítaj doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.91,0:00:41.95,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Kvôli slnku som sa necítila dobre tak som zaspala.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.93,0:00:45.15,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Dáš si kávu? Dám postaviť vodu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.60,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:49.37,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:51.18,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Tvoje sliny.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.72,0:00:54.58,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, eh! Máš pravdu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.82,0:00:55.88,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:56.81,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Čo je?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.35,0:00:59.25,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Máš priateľa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:02.77,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Prečo sa ma na to pýtaš tak náhle?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.01,0:01:05.41,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, len zo zvedavosti...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:07.83,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Bože! Ty si divný.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.60,0:01:14.15,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Ak by mala priateľa...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.08,0:01:19.83,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,Bola by jej spiaca oslintaná tvár taká roztomilá?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:02:51.26,AKT,,0000,0000,0000,,
